  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Tre Isole</strong> is where you'll have breakfast and has lovely lake views, which you can enjoy while you eat. Breakfast is buffet style with hot and cold options.</p>
<p><strong>The Bar</strong> is open during the day and the evening and is a great place to have a nightcap after dinner.</p>
<p>The hotels a la carte restaurant is available for dinner (bookable and payable locally).</p>]]></cateringDescription>
