  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The art deco building of the Grand Hotel Bristol sits on Stresa's lakefront promenade. It's wonderfully elegant with stained-glass ceilings in the lobby and old-world rooms. Spend time relaxing by the pool in the gardens or on the restaurant terrace where you'll get views of the Borromean Islands.</p>
<p> </p>]]></listingDescription>
