  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms</strong> sleep two people. They have a traditional décor with wooden floors. Rooms can have a double bed on request and facilities include air conditioning, TV, safe, hairdryer and a bath with a shower head (shower, on request).</p>
<p><strong> Pool, side lake view &amp; full lake view rooms</strong> are available for a supplement. These rooms have a balcony. Interconnecting lake view rooms are also available on request. </p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are also available. Single rooms with lake or pool views and a balcony are available for a supplement.</p>
<p><em>Please note that a balcony room can only be guaranteed if you are staying in a room with pool or side lake views and full lake views.</em></p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
